[:en] # About Mega Fortune<br>
Mega Fortune has already become one of the classic jackpot games. Just like the name suggests the game offers the possibility to win an enormous jackpot. Two of the paid out Mega Fortune jackpots have entered the Guinness Book of Records as the largest jackpot wins with amounts of over €10 million.</li>
</ul>
<p>Mega Fortune takes you on a cruise of luxury. In true jet set spirit among yachts, diamonds, limousines and expensive Champagne you spin away towards a spectacular wheel of fortune where you have the chance to hit one out of three jackpots. With three different special features you can be sure that this slot gives you an adrenalin-filled gaming experience.</p>
<h2 id="game-features">Game Features</h2>
<p>The game consists of five wheels with three symbols on each. In addition to the regular winning combinations there are also three different special symbols.</p>
<h3 id="wild-2">Wild</h3>
<p>When you hit the luxury yacht it acts like the common wild: it replaces all the other symbols except the scatter and bonus symbols.</p>
<h3 id="free-spins">Free Spins</h3>
<p>In the case of hitting three or more Champagne bottles you are awarded with 10 Free Spins in which you have an active win multiplier of 1-5 times. If you hit two or more bottles during the Free Spins you’ll receive an additional 5 Free Spins.</p>
<h3 id="the-bonus-game">The Bonus Game</h3>
<p>When at least three of the wheel of fortune symbols with the text BONUS on them hit a winning bet line you are transported into the jackpot game. Whilst in there you choose when to start the spinning of the wheel that consists of three different circles that represents three different jackpot levels – RAPID, MAJOR and MEGA jackpot. Luck, or faith, decides whether you’ll win a jackpot. At the top of the game you can find the different jackpot amounts updating in real time.</p>
<p>The reason why this jackpot is so incredibly huge is that it’s a so-called progressive jackpot. This means that several different online casinos all contribute to building up the jackpot size. In turn this enables a very rapid jackpot growth and a bigger possibility for you to become a millionaire.</p>
